descriptionHtml:
Players home.

You can teleport to MORVAIN, see picture for info on location for MORVAIN, click on MORVAIN on map then teleport.

I have tested the navmesh with a follower and encountered no problems.

[b]Requirements:[/b] Dawnguard.Hearthfire.Dragonborn.

[b]Installation:[/b] Just download with Nexus mod manger, Mod organizer or manual,if you want to install it manually,
                    then you have to extract it into your data file for Skyrim.

[b]
Unistallation:[/b]  Just untick in mod manger or mod organzier or delete the files you manually installed.


[b]CREDITS:[/b]  Many thanks to   "cad435 for Snow Elves Remastered"                                              


I hope you enjoy the home,this will be my last mod for sometime.

My Regards to you all.

Thank You.
